收皮，拜鳩拜"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T01:26:21.000Z","msg":"可以吹多一兩句<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好多</span>，唔係人地當你煩膠"},{"pid":"1aa11a0f7c2343bf0e063e33d1d6ea7e9098c72c","tid":1929312,"uid":89064,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T01:33:47.000Z","msg":"試過搭訕識過3個女仔(有contact冇下文)"},{"pid":"e74d0ff619201bf278c88bd3c8b011633207b933","tid":1929312,"uid":217228,"like":3,"dislike":9,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T01:56:24.000Z","msg":"路人成功率應該得幾% , 比著係你3唔識7 突然有條友話想同你做FD 都唔會彩佢啦 <br />\n<br />\n1. 建議要識就識D店員<br />\n2. 扮拍video / 訪問"},{"pid":"3b36d9e6d3e89caf35689270fa8567d7ef768021","tid":1929312,"uid":149563,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T03:58:20.000Z","msg":"有friend試過成功咗<br />\n不過佢係靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a7ed7a2258b111a9e93d314299f821af0f749d5","tid":1929312,"uid":228213,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T07:29:20.000Z","msg":"樣就一定要嘅， 但係每個人嘅標準唔一樣，你打扮一下，都會有人肯嘅。<br />\n<br />\n然後就係簡單表達係你自己想做咩， 直接啲就得。<br />\n<br />\n其實好多人根本冇做過呢樣嘢 ，會有好多恐懼同誤解， 你自己試下就會搵到經驗， 同埋冇想像中咁恐怖。"},{"pid":"c38ccfafa60eebcc92170ed56871d3dc7224517b","tid":1929312,"uid":39710,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T07:30:31.000Z","msg":"你的樣子如何"},{"pid":"bea190ddfad5eb1e87d38a7d9555379998f993bb","tid":1929312,"uid":324020,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T11:21:07.000Z","msg":"中學試過係街俾人問可唔可以做個朋友<br />\n第一次俾人咁問嚇到我呆咗即刻走<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n三唔識七，無啦啦咁問我當咗佢係變態佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50be6517dbb924f172499f1013c0d09076379c06","tid":1929312,"uid":192409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T01:07:00.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"6fc531c0e15c254124a4ceddc3385fac289af221","tid":1929312,"uid":48077,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T01:15:09.00